ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectPIAPOT BAND ** SETTING APART ** (LED-09-09)
PrecisSetting apart of 129.078 hectares of surface lands, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Piapot Band, located in the Rural Municipality of Elmsthorpe No. 100, near the village of Truax, Saskatchewan, as an addition to PIAPOT INDIAN RESERVE No. 75.
